text: Andru H. Volinsky (born March 13, 1956) is an American Democratic politician. He was a member of the Executive Council of New Hampshire, representing the 2nd District from 2017 until 2021. Volinsky unsuccessfully ran for Governor of New Hampshire in the 2020 election. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Lawyers from New York City Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from New York City Category:Politicians from New Hampshire Category:Democratic Party (United States) politicians Category:Lawyers from New Hampshire
